message: IM INJECTING VOLTAGE ON PP3V3_S0 AND WITH MY THERMAL CAMERA I CAN SEE THAT PCH IS GETTING WARM... IS THAT NORMAL BEHAVIOR WHEN INJECTING VOLTAGE? OR DOES IT MEANS THAT PCH IS DEAD?

What's the reason to inject voltage into 3K power rail?
